ound) and fight (yup, you can melee with your staff while waiting for the spell to go off) tends to make things much more exciting. I've been really enjoying it so far and with a keyboard chatting is pretty easy.<br>
<br>
Oh one other thing, instead of sitting to regain hp/mana, you now buy food/water. food/water works just like a spell/ability in that you get a little icon showing that you're buffed with it, but it goes away as soon as you either 1) get back to full power/hp, 2) attack something, 3) cast a spell. Anyway, while that food/water buff is on you, you regen power/hp much faster than just sitting around. very useful!!<br>
